你能够调用以下的API:
[['BankReportSearch.find_financial_reports', {'name': 'BankReportSearch.find_financial_reports', 'description': 'This function searches for financial reports of a bank based on the bank name and specified years.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'bankName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the bank.'}, {'name': 'years', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of years for which reports are required.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'reports', 'description': 'A list of up to three financial reports for the specified bank and years.'}]}], ['BankReportAnalysis.analyze_financial_ratios', {'name': 'BankReportAnalysis.analyze_financial_ratios', 'description': 'This function analyzes financial ratios from bank reports.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'ratios', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of ratios to analyze, e.g., assetLiabilityRatio, netProfitMargin.'}, {'name': 'reports', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of report IDs to analyze.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'analysis', 'description': 'An analysis of the selected financial ratios from the reports.'}]}], ['StockMarketData.get_stock_history', {'name': 'StockMarketData.get_stock_history', 'description': 'This function retrieves historical stock data for a bank.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'bankSymbol', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The stock symbol of the bank.'}, {'name': 'duration', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The duration for which stock history is required.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'history', 'description': 'Historical stock data for the specified bank and duration.'}]}], ['FinancialHealthAssessment.generate_report', {'name': 'FinancialHealthAssessment.generate_report', 'description': 'This function generates a financial health assessment report for a bank.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'bankName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the bank.'}, {'name': 'ratiosAnalysis', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the ratios analysis.'}, {'name': 'stockHistory', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the stock history data.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'report', 'description': 'A financial health assessment report for the bank.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `BankReportSearch.find_financial_reports` 并传入 `bankName` 和 `years`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "BankReportSearch.find_financial_reports",
    "args": "{'bankName': 'GlobalTrust Bank', 'years': [2020, 2021, 2022]}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
